Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.76,0:01:05.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They're gaining!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.74,0:01:21.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.68,0:01:22.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isame!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.15,0:01:27.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Can you move?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.35,0:01:28.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just a scratch.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:30.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Go on without me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.25,0:01:31.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN A] Lower your weapons.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.69,0:01:37.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN B] Listen and obey, you two.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.66,0:01:39.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You and your brother are damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.63,0:01:44.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN C] We cannot allow this to continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.40,0:01:46.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN B] Uphold the code.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.40,0:01:49.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN C] The code of Fuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.11,0:01:51.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN A] Lower your weapons now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.14,0:01:53.31,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I can keep them at bay while you run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.34,0:01:54.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't stay here for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.71,0:01:57.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm not running anywhere like this. You run.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.31,0:01:58.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.45,0:02:01.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN A] One must die if the other wishes to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.52,0:02:03.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Balance must be restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.02,0:02:06.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,End your misfortune before it worsens.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.62,0:02:10.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,One cannot truly breathe until the other breaths no more.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.66,0:02:13.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN B] None are above the code.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN A] One may endure...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.40,0:02:17.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,End your life... Or end your brother's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.05,0:02:31.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN B yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.65,0:02:34.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN B grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO] Isuke. Isame.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.37,0:02:53.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN C grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.51,0:02:59.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:02.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSINS grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.11,0:03:03.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN C] You traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.51,0:03:05.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Father needs us! We have to help him!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:07.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'll help him. You run!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.72,0:03:10.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No, Mother! We're not leaving either of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.69,0:03:16.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Do as I say! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.69,0:03:19.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.63,0:03:20.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.88,0:03:37.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] This is my fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.25,0:03:39.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No one would have discovered us if I hadn't decided
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.45,0:03:42.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,to follow you out of that forsaken cave.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.35,0:03:43.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.72,0:03:46.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I could've have stopped you, but I didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.46,0:03:47.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm the one to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.73,0:03:52.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But we're going to be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.83,0:03:59.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] They're still out there...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.60,0:04:01.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What if we never see either of them again?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.77,0:04:03.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] They'll find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.27,0:04:06.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is that them?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN A] There you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.82,0:04:16.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Go, Isame!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.22,0:04:18.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Isuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.73,0:04:29.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isame!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.60,0:04:36.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ASSASSIN A] Your births were a curse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.87,0:04:38.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You are unwanted and wicked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.75,0:04:46.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,For the Fuuma to survive, you must die. For the--
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.35,0:04:47.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:01.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isame! Isuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.60,0:05:02.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.70,0:05:03.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.77,0:05:07.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're all right now. My brave boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.57,0:05:10.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm so happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:12.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.21,0:05:16.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The hereafter doesn't have any use for our secrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:18.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You had to kill your comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.71,0:05:20.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,All because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.48,0:05:21.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I did this to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.92,0:05:22.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.85,0:05:25.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He's wrong. It was my fault. I saw him--
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.49,0:05:27.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO] Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.56,0:05:28.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.49,0:05:29.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And Isame.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.66,0:05:30.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:40.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The fallen presented you with a choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.50,0:05:42.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They wanted you to kill yourselves or one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.44,0:05:49.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Neither considered putting themselves before their brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.85,0:05:51.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And you were willing to sacrifice everything
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.01,0:05:52.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,as a result.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:57.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The two of you are both one and the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.62,0:06:00.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You are brothers living a sole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.42,0:06:04.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where one draws breath, the other exhales it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.26,0:06:05.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Never forget the love that gives you
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.93,0:06:07.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,this unparalleled edge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:12.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME, ISUKE crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.30,0:06:13.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO] Remember this day.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.18,0:08:43.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MITSU grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.19,0:08:51.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MITSU yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.80,0:08:55.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MITSU] Curse you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.13,0:08:56.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[groans] Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.87,0:09:00.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How do you keep managing to best the two of us, Isuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.17,0:09:01.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I had him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.24,0:09:04.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Okay. Maybe that's a lie, but we're getting closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.21,0:09:08.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Closer isn't near enough. I want to defeat him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.01,0:09:10.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Might I suggest making moves that aren't
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:12.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,entirely predictable?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.18,0:09:15.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ITSUKI] That's a curious blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.45,0:09:17.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Did you craft it yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.69,0:09:18.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.92,0:09:21.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It comes in pretty handy in the heat of battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.76,0:09:23.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That so?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.13,0:09:25.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,One weapon makes such a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:28.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Huh? Look who it is. Nanao.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.53,0:09:29.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't she be training?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.10,0:09:33.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ITSUKI] She should be a lot of things,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.94,0:09:35.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,but the ceremony changed her.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.87,0:09:39.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Nanao was happier before.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.07,0:09:42.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.21,0:09:43.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The target was her mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.79,0:09:56.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] You've become a true Fuuma now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.83,0:09:58.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,and yet you seem distraught.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.69,0:09:59.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Over here! Nanao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.17,0:10:06.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NANAO] I suppose... I should feel content.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.77,0:10:09.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I still feel her blood warming me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.04,0:10:10.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Her tremble at the realization.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.11,0:10:15.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I thought the box would confine the guilt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.58,0:10:17.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But its clutches hold me still.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.12,0:10:22.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NISHIKI] There you are, Sister!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:27.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[NANAO] Just a moment. I'll be down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.89,0:10:32.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,May she never have to feel the death of her heart as I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.56,0:11:03.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Curse you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.90,0:11:07.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.80,0:11:12.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[door slides]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.94,0:11:16.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isame. May I come in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.21,0:11:17.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.94,0:11:19.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How did it fair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:23.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.71,0:11:25.31,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The weight makes for a perfect throw.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's impressive.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.28,0:11:30.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Well then, it seems my efforts weren't for naught, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:38.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] What troubles you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:40.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.73,0:11:43.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We share the same face, Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.37,0:11:45.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm well aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.27,0:11:49.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So I tend to know what our expressions mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.97,0:11:52.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Rite of Passage claimed another.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.14,0:11:55.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But the ceremony has changed this one.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The target was their mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.18,0:11:59.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.08,0:12:03.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But still, anything easily gained... is easily lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.22,0:12:05.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Still bothersome?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.19,0:12:08.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hardly. I barely notice it anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.02,0:12:10.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I manage just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.86,0:12:13.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[door slides]
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.70,0:12:19.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA] Hope you have an appetite.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:22.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sorry I took so long getting here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.91,0:12:25.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Am I interrupting?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.11,0:12:28.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isuke, were you wanting to eat down here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.38,0:12:29.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.21,0:12:31.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your father has been looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.41,0:12:32.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.35,0:12:41.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Be sure to eat it quickly before it gets cold, honey.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.09,0:12:45.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Look at those hands of yours. They're filthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.13,0:12:46.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] They're fine, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.30,0:12:50.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA chuckles] And I suppose this smudge is fine, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.20,0:12:51.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:12:58.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.44,0:12:59.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You have a mission.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.15,0:13:05.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.77,0:13:29.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Looks pretty safe to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.04,0:13:30.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.91,0:13:32.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That bothers you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.24,0:13:34.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Our numbers are too great for such a task.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.84,0:13:35.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.74,0:13:37.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I have to remind myself that no number
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.95,0:13:40.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,is too great for Master Kotarou Fuuma the 9th.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.49,0:13:45.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[sizzling]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.72,0:13:46.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.76,0:13:48.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[sizzling continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.39,0:13:52.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARDS gasp, yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.80,0:13:58.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARD C] It's an ambush! We're under attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:13:59.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARD D] Protect the Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.30,0:14:01.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Time for action!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.27,0:14:07.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.28,0:14:11.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.98,0:14:14.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Someone stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.52,0:14:18.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[PORTERS gasp, grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.96,0:14:22.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TRAITOR A] Let it end.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.36,0:14:29.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'd say that's about enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.17,0:14:36.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.77,0:14:39.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARDS grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.48,0:14:43.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Master. He's been seized.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.45,0:14:49.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] Your skill is that of a shinobi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.02,0:14:52.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where does your allegiance lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.49,0:14:53.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA ELDER A] Answer him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:16.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[striking] --[TRAITOR A grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.95,0:15:18.31,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[blood spatters]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.35,0:15:20.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[grunting continues]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.46,0:15:33.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA ELDER A] I felt depraved eyes stalking us,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.60,0:15:35.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,but I never would've imagined it to be the work
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.86,0:15:37.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,of one of our own...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:41.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sacrilege! You dishonor the clan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.04,0:15:43.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TRAITOR A coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.34,0:15:45.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--Do it now. --Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.04,0:15:50.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TRAITOR A coughing]
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.61,0:15:52.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA ELDER A] Did you act alone?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.05,0:15:53.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How many are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.39,0:15:59.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What did you say, traitor?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.55,0:16:01.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Speak up before I--!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.63,0:16:06.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.26,0:16:07.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] Calm yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He made his point.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.37,0:16:12.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Now make mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.44,0:16:18.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Finish this, Eishiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.41,0:16:28.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TRAITOR A] You disgrace the title of Kotarou Fuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.95,0:16:30.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Silence! That is your master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.02,0:16:32.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Traitor!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.19,0:16:34.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I am a Fuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.19,0:16:36.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My allegiance is to the Lord Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.46,0:16:38.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Can you say the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.13,0:16:41.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His resurrection approaches and you do nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:43.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Nothing but ceremony after ceremony...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.57,0:16:45.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where is your loyalty?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:48.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How many must we lose until you're satisfied?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.34,0:16:49.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This isn't for our Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.64,0:16:52.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We are drenched in the blood of Fuuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.04,0:16:53.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,All for your own self-indulgence!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.01,0:16:56.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You will answer to the Lord Orochi for your sins
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.04,0:16:57.31,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,unforgivable!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.18,0:17:05.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Pathetic. You show defiance rather than penance
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.25,0:17:07.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,in your last moments.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.06,0:17:10.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And you dare speak to me of our Lord Orochi's intentions.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.59,0:17:11.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Eishiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.93,0:17:16.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Kill this conspirator right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.10,0:17:20.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Eishiro. I failed them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.94,0:17:23.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to protect the young from the Rite of Passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.51,0:17:27.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They're undeserving of such a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.21,0:17:31.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,To carry that hell... No one deserves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.95,0:17:34.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You understand that I had to try for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.38,0:17:37.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[knife thrust] --[TRAITOR A gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.36,0:17:46.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.47,0:18:00.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Let the animals have his traitorous corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.12,0:18:13.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA ELDER A] What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.26,0:18:17.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Where are you going with his--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.37,0:18:31.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is it finished?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.62,0:18:51.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What reason would a Fuuma have to attack their master?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.63,0:18:53.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.40,0:18:54.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.53,0:18:58.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Do you know what it means to be one of the Fuuma clan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.17,0:19:00.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Fuuma live to serve Lord Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:03.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What purpose does your life carry knowing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.14,0:19:06.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] My purpose is... serve Lord Orochi, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO] Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.24,0:19:10.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That's the purpose each of us was born into.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.25,0:19:11.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Inherited across generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.05,0:19:18.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What purpose do you wish for?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.35,0:19:19.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.59,0:19:25.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're indebted.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.43,0:19:27.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Copious blood has been spilled so that Isame and I
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.70,0:19:29.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,may continue to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.26,0:19:32.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're beholden to our fallen Fuuma brethren.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.37,0:19:34.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Becoming a fledged Fuuma may ease their apprehensions
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.67,0:19:35.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,in the afterlife, and--
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.84,0:19:38.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO] That is not a wish, Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.31,0:19:39.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That is duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:42.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You ask too much of yourself and it worries me, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:43.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:44.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO] Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.45,0:19:48.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What do you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.82,0:19:54.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.29,0:19:58.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I want to be with my family.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:19:59.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You, Mother, and Isame.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:02.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I want to lead a life of contentment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.66,0:20:04.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Here with those I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:08.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Same for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.60,0:20:37.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.22,0:20:59.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Explain yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.55,0:21:01.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isame... Did you hit Mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.26,0:21:09.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What am I to her?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.20,0:21:11.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Some pampered domesticated animal?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.51,0:21:22.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She had the gall to say I was growing up so fast--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.58,0:21:23.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,that she was proud of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.81,0:21:26.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Can you believe that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.51,0:21:27.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Pitiable.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.35,0:21:32.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She calls this growing up?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.19,0:21:33.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My, how I've grown while sealed away
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:35.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,from the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.76,0:21:38.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What is there for her to be proud of?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:41.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mother doesn't see isolation for what it truly--
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.63,0:21:44.30,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Did you lay hands on our mother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.33,0:21:47.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't blame me. She was in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.84,0:21:49.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I was just trying to get my tools from her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.47,0:21:53.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mother doesn't want me working on anything for you
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.64,0:21:55.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,or the clan anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.98,0:21:57.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Perhaps she has a point.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.35,0:22:00.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.55,0:22:06.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's all I have to combat the emptiness inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.96,0:22:10.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,At least with this tremendous envy, I feel something, Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.63,0:22:13.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The weapons I craft are for me, not you!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:17.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Soon you'll be a fully fledged Fuuma
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.57,0:22:19.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,and forget this poor reflection...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.80,0:22:20.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And where will I be?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.94,0:22:25.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Stuck in this tomb with a hand that won't stop shaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.51,0:22:27.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Did it shake then?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.24,0:22:29.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,When you struck our mother, did your hand shake?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.58,0:22:30.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME gasps]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.42,0:22:35.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[BOTH grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.42,0:22:37.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--Isame! --Get off of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.92,0:22:39.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Listen to me, Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.45,0:22:41.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You are not a poor reflection!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.26,0:22:46.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.86,0:22:48.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What have I done to deserve this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.86,0:22:52.47,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.77,0:22:58.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA ELDER C] New unfledged brothers and sisters
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.04,0:23:00.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,have been selected for the Rite of Passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.81,0:23:06.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,None of their ritual targets are of blood or bond.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.65,0:23:07.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes... Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.95,0:23:10.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sir, there've been unforeseen repercussions.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.52,0:23:12.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The young woman who ended her mother's life
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.35,0:23:13.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,still suffers greatly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.79,0:23:17.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] She suffers because she's weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:21.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Rite of Passage is not for the frail or the fragile.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.63,0:23:24.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,To kill those we cherish above all serves to fortify
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.47,0:23:26.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,a true Fuuma's resolve.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.40,0:23:30.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Rework the targets immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.51,0:23:33.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.69,0:23:50.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO] What do you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.46,0:23:56.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] I want to lead a life a contentment...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.36,0:23:57.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Here with those I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.47,0:24:01.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] What have I done to deserve this?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.11,0:24:06.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ITSUKI] Isuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.74,0:24:08.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.88,0:24:10.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MITSU] Another ceremony.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.04,0:24:11.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] What? Why so soon?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.75,0:24:13.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,One took place not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.82,0:24:15.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Was it someone we knew?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.42,0:24:16.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Who was the target?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.66,0:24:28.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.37,0:24:34.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] You've done well, child...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.47,0:24:37.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You will now confine yourself within six walls
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.61,0:24:39.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,for seven rises and falls.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.81,0:24:45.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,A true Fuuma doesn't waste a death.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.88,0:24:48.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Embrace the darkness and endure.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.53,0:25:06.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How long before it's one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.43,0:25:08.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We'll have our time. It's an honor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:08.87,0:25:12.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's an honor to kill a loved one?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.81,0:25:14.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That isn't what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.88,0:25:18.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just the thought sickens me.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.11,0:25:21.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But... it is our Rite of Passage...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:21.42,0:25:24.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No Fuuma can ignore the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.85,0:25:27.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MITSU] You say that, but this hasn't always been
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.12,0:25:28.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,the way of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.89,0:25:31.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Kill someone dear,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.56,0:25:34.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,be sealed in a box for seven days and seven nights.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.73,0:25:37.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Shroud yourself in darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.10,0:25:38.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It was the Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.70,0:25:41.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He found the Rite of Passage within an ancient text.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:41.44,0:25:43.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He's responsible for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.17,0:25:44.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ITSUKI] I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:44.67,0:25:46.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MITSU] I... I fail to see his reasoning...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.81,0:25:48.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We've seen what the ceremony has done to others.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.88,0:25:53.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Being Fuuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.51,0:25:54.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is that what you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.89,0:25:59.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Obviously.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.55,0:26:01.99,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Not that we have say in the matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.02,0:26:04.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MITSU] Isn't that what you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.53,0:26:05.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] What I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.93,0:26:07.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MESSENGER A] Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.66,0:26:10.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I must speak with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.90,0:26:12.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Privately, I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.21,0:26:19.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.96,0:26:43.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Rikka...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.23,0:26:47.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA] Eishiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.60,0:26:50.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.71,0:26:54.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.78,0:26:56.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO] I wish I knew.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.04,0:26:57.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.96,0:27:10.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[door slides]
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.99,0:27:14.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Can't be Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.96,0:27:17.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She hasn't visited me for quite some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.63,0:27:19.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.80,0:27:24.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The ceremony claimed more family.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.74,0:27:25.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Another Fuuma lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.84,0:27:31.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And then? Is there more?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.68,0:27:33.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The girl who murdered her mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.71,0:27:36.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,She had a younger sister she shielded from this.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.85,0:27:39.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It was the person she tried to protect that ended her...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.79,0:27:41.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Her own sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.22,0:27:42.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hardly surprising...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.96,0:27:44.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is this what has you so upset?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.03,0:27:49.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Remember yourself, Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:49.13,0:27:51.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This is what it takes to be Fuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.60,0:27:55.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What it takes... Could you do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.00,0:27:58.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Without hesitation.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.21,0:27:59.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Were the target Mother or Father,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.81,0:28:02.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,you wouldn't hesitate in the slightest?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.08,0:28:03.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't be absurd...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.88,0:28:07.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They're extraordinary ninjas, far too valuable.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.35,0:28:09.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Fuuma would be crippled without our parents.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.85,0:28:15.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'd kill another.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.36,0:28:18.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I would end you without a second thought wasted
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.23,0:28:20.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,should duty demand it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.60,0:28:23.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How easily you forget our debt, fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.10,0:28:24.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I haven't forgotten...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.73,0:28:27.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--Fuuma died! --[ISUKE] I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.17,0:28:29.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The price owed weighs heavier and heavier on me
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.90,0:28:31.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,with every passing sunset.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.01,0:28:35.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Honor and duty demand I become a Fuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.88,0:28:36.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But I--
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.68,0:28:39.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.91,0:28:42.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Another's misfortune carries no influence.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.68,0:28:44.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You should be stuck here!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.09,0:28:47.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[rumbling]
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.72,0:28:50.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Stay here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:51.26,0:28:54.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[clanging]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.23,0:29:01.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Itsuki! Mitsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.00,0:29:03.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.64,0:29:05.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,There was a massive explosion.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.27,0:29:06.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Looks to be deliberate.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.77,0:29:07.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARD E] You there!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.84,0:29:09.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The master's being moved to safety!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.64,0:29:10.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We need more people!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.75,0:29:11.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.95,0:29:13.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARD I] Who could be doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.18,0:29:14.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARD J] No one knows!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.28,0:29:15.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARD F] Find the attacker!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.69,0:29:19.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MAN A screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.09,0:29:21.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[shattering]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.12,0:29:23.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARDS grunt]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:24.86,0:29:26.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARD J] Surrender or die!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.31,0:29:46.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hurry! The assassin is here!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.45,0:29:47.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:49.08,0:29:50.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.35,0:29:51.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[ISUKE] Master! --[HEAD FUUMA] Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.82,0:29:53.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,By any means necessary!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.05,0:29:54.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--Sir! --Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:05.43,0:30:07.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--He's fast. --Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.37,0:30:15.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARDS grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.36,0:30:30.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GUARDS yell]
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.44,0:30:43.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[MITSU] Isuke! --[ITSUKI] Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.13,0:31:08.90,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're one of us, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.93,0:31:10.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're a Fuuma too.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.18,0:31:23.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So it shall be.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:55.18,0:31:59.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Was there an explosion? I could hear it from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.18,0:32:01.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that you're always waiting on me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.55,0:32:07.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] You're not going to tell me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.56,0:32:09.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is my existence so insignificant that you can't
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.96,0:32:11.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,be bothered with a simple question?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:15.96,0:32:20.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.97,0:32:22.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.04,0:32:25.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.61,0:32:27.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mother, please... Can you just talk to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.52,0:32:45.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.86,0:32:50.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.44,0:32:58.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.48,0:33:06.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please don't do this...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:06.31,0:33:07.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why, Father?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.98,0:33:11.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The bleeding isn't stopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.99,0:33:14.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Father... Father!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.46,0:33:17.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO] Isuke. Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:17.39,0:33:20.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You have to take my body back to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.09,0:33:22.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You have to finish it, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.46,0:33:24.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I've failed you...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.43,0:33:29.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I didn't want this.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.60,0:33:31.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I wanted to give you something better.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:34.64,0:33:35.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Father...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.94,0:33:37.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Remember your wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:37.41,0:33:42.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,For life, love, and happiness with family.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.42,0:33:43.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Without you?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:45.02,0:33:47.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[EISHIRO] Take care of our family.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.92,0:33:50.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your mother and brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:50.09,0:33:51.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,They need you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.70,0:34:04.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE sobbing]
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.36,0:34:27.66,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] Isuke comes from good Fuuma stock.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.70,0:34:29.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I think he will do very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:29.63,0:34:31.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA ELDER B] Yes, sir. Though...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.37,0:34:34.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I would be remiss were I not to voice my concern.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.10,0:34:34.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.00,0:34:36.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,As you may recall, your masked attacker
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.00,0:34:39.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,was never brought to justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.41,0:34:41.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Was it not Isuke himself who followed
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.28,0:34:44.61,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,this mysterious foe, one quite skilled in our ways?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.65,0:34:46.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And his stare...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.15,0:34:50.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Something changed after he pursued the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.05,0:34:51.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Malice resides.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.17,0:35:41.34,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] Shrouded in darkness, he emerges
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.37,0:35:42.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,a true Fuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.67,0:35:46.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Honor your family and serve your master well.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.71,0:35:47.71,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.10,0:36:13.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Keep an eye on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.63,0:36:14.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.65,0:36:33.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:33.75,0:36:36.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please know. I'll protect our family--
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.16,0:36:37.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You and Isame, just as Father wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.83,0:36:39.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,As I promised.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.10,0:36:46.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA crying]
Dialogue: 0,0:37:00.71,0:37:01.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Isame.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.35,0:37:06.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.36,0:37:12.43,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It's done.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.46,0:37:13.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:19.80,0:37:22.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'm starving. Any food?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.19,0:37:46.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Why is your food untouched?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.93,0:37:49.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You were suffering...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.66,0:37:51.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How could I possibly eat when my brother
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.40,0:37:53.37,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,was ensnared in bottomless misery?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.91,0:38:04.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please forgive me.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.68,0:38:07.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Another's misfortune carries no influence!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.48,0:38:09.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You shoud be stuck here!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.38,0:38:10.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You knew then.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.45,0:38:13.29,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You came to me for peace of mind and found nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.32,0:38:14.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I... I should've realized.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.62,0:38:17.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I failed you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.46,0:38:23.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What do you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.37,0:38:28.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Father once asked me that question.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.30,0:38:30.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Not my purpose as a warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.24,0:38:32.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He wished to know what I wanted for my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.91,0:38:35.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What I want...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.48,0:38:38.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Being Fuuma would be enough, but... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.85,0:38:40.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] So be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.08,0:38:45.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If being Fuuma is your desire, then I'll see to it myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.22,0:38:47.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And I won't rely on an antiquated ritual, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.82,0:38:49.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Things have to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.36,0:38:51.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'll see to that, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.43,0:38:52.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isame...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.53,0:38:54.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Change favors risk over reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.83,0:38:57.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The last thing father did was ask me to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.36,0:38:58.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,the pair of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.00,0:39:01.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I see now that Mother is already lost to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.74,0:39:02.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No, she's not.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.90,0:39:05.17,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Yes, she is. Believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.28,0:39:09.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'll never see her smile again.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.58,0:39:13.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Father's gone... He's dead because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.55,0:39:16.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.95,0:39:19.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Protect her.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.65,0:39:22.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] How did you answer Father's question?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.92,0:39:24.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.26,0:39:25.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] What is it you really want?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.33,0:39:30.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I wanted fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.03,0:39:32.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I wanted to find happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.30,0:39:35.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I wanted my family there at my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.57,0:39:36.74,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He liked that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.61,0:39:39.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I miss him.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.84,0:39:44.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Isame.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.65,0:39:48.42,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Keep this with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.45,0:39:49.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It belonged to Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.98,0:39:51.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You want me to have it?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.42,0:39:52.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.72,0:39:54.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Consider it a symbol.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:54.49,0:39:55.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your wish will be realized, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.99,0:39:59.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I promise you. Even if mine can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.79,0:40:02.26,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] It will.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:02.30,0:40:03.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We are both one in the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.61,0:41:28.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA A] Please see reason!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.08,0:41:30.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochi's resurrection draws closer, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.88,0:41:33.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Why must we hesitate in preparation?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.05,0:41:35.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Master. We require orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.79,0:41:36.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.86,0:41:39.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How many times must I entertain my subordinates
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.73,0:41:42.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,questioning the highest Fuuma authority?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.60,0:41:44.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA B] With all due respect,
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.13,0:41:47.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,the highest Fuuma authority is Lord Orochi. He would not want--
Dialogue: 0,0:41:47.63,0:41:49.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] He is not here!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:51.41,0:41:53.54,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,All is in service of Our Lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.57,0:41:56.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,To think otherwise tarnishes Fuuma and Lord Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.94,0:41:59.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He demands the Rite of Passage, for the Great Serpent
Dialogue: 0,0:41:59.45,0:42:01.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,requires only true ninjas!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:05.45,0:42:09.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I am Kotarou Fuuma the 9th and you will respect that title.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.59,0:42:11.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,To question my methods is to question
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.16,0:42:12.86,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,the great Lord Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.62,0:42:44.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA] You're in for a treat today.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.93,0:42:46.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You like trout, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.83,0:42:52.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] This is kind of you, Mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.60,0:42:55.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Would you...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.80,0:42:56.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I would like if...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.84,0:43:00.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I would love the pleasure of your company today.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.51,0:43:03.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[door slides]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:12.89,0:43:16.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA C] Isuke... No... You're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.69,0:43:21.70,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MITSU] Shall I feign surprise?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.73,0:43:24.97,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The master isn't even listening to his advisors anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:25.00,0:43:29.14,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ITSUKI] It's rather clear you don't agree with him, Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.17,0:43:31.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hell... I'm surprised you didn't voice your disapproval
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.97,0:43:35.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,at the gathering. It's not like you to keep quiet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.51,0:43:37.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My words do not carry true weight yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.91,0:43:41.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sadly he does have a point, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.62,0:43:43.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The feeble haven't a place here.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.12,0:43:45.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochi deserves to be served by those who are true
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.52,0:43:47.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,to the cause...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.09,0:43:49.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,But his tactics are maddening.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.72,0:43:51.02,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,This has to end.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.19,0:43:57.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] The Rite of Passage will be no more when I become master.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.66,0:43:58.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You sound certain.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.00,0:44:03.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You'll make a fine leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.14,0:44:06.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Damn right you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.72,0:44:19.09,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That noise... Did you hear something over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.12,0:44:21.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hm? Not really.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.15,0:44:22.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ITSUKI] Pay it no mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.99,0:44:26.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The cliffs often distort all kinds of noises near there.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.83,0:44:30.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[MITSU] Huh? Wait! --[ITSUKI] Isuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.77,0:44:36.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.10,0:44:38.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[ISAME] Mother! --[blows landing]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.14,0:44:39.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--Stop it! --[blows landing]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.67,0:44:41.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:44:41.81,0:44:43.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.28,0:44:45.08,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Unhand me this instant!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.11,0:44:47.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just leave her alone, please...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.81,0:44:51.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your hiding of this aberration shows brazen disloyalty
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.18,0:44:52.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,to the whole clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.75,0:44:56.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your fate and his suffering are now intertwined.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.99,0:44:58.89,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA] Please don't hurt him.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.93,0:45:01.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Show him mercy, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.23,0:45:02.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.70,0:45:06.67,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mercy is weakness!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.80,0:45:10.60,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA screams]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.64,0:45:11.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Stop it! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.84,0:45:14.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If you want to hurt someone, let it be me!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.88,0:45:16.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Mother, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.98,0:45:25.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] Show her progeny the same courtesy then end him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.22,0:45:26.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA ELDER B] Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.22,0:45:28.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA] Please, Master...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.06,0:45:33.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He has promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.06,0:45:35.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Let him prove his worth.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.66,0:45:37.16,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Spare my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.20,0:45:38.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The blame lies solely with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.00,0:45:45.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] Rikka. He is lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.97,0:45:47.24,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Just as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.41,0:45:52.75,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA screaming]
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.18,0:45:56.82,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No! Mother!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.03,0:46:09.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:46:12.07,0:46:15.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA] Isame! You have to let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.30,0:46:17.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,No! I won't!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.04,0:46:19.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA] Isame... You need to let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.89,0:46:37.96,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[RIKKA] My brave boys. I'm so happy to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:40.99,0:46:42.36,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.47,0:46:54.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] The flame should have you both.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.31,0:46:55.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You are damned.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.84,0:46:58.28,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I will not allow either of you another day.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.38,0:47:01.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ITSUKI] Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.98,0:47:04.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[MITSU] Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:04.08,0:47:06.32,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please forgive him.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.35,0:47:09.69,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Please. Isuke is too valuable to lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.72,0:47:11.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Master... Please, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.46,0:47:15.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Weakness.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:24.50,0:47:27.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ITSUKI, MITSU choking]
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.98,0:47:31.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.95,0:47:33.01,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] Monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.05,0:47:35.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Insolence obliges consequence.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.15,0:47:37.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The fate of all Fuuma, fledged or not,
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.25,0:47:39.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,falls to me and me alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:47:47.23,0:47:49.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] You alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.43,0:47:52.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You claim to do all this in the name of Fuuma?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:52.27,0:47:54.80,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,That this is the will of the Great Serpent?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.87,0:48:00.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your mother spent the last of my patience.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.14,0:48:02.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What is said by the Kotarou Fuuma is law!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.98,0:48:04.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hold your tongue and you might not share
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.01,0:48:06.48,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,your brother's fate!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.51,0:48:08.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Lord Orochi will condemn this...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.92,0:48:10.38,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His resurrection will prove that all--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.42,0:48:12.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] I don't care about the damn Orochi!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.23,0:48:23.46,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA] The purpose of the Fuuma clan is to protect
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.50,0:48:25.83,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,their master no matter the cost.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.87,0:48:28.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Obey his will above all others!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.10,0:48:30.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And I demand that you end his life!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:39.41,0:48:41.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Your judgment...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.45,0:48:43.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...is unbefitting of the Fuuma clan.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.26,0:48:53.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The time has come...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.23,0:48:55.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...for a new Fuuma master.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.91,0:49:07.91,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,--[FUUMA ELDER C] Master! --[HEAD FUUMA] Kill him!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:12.95,0:49:15.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there! Hurry and--
Dialogue: 0,0:49:18.99,0:49:20.15,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He must be stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.19,0:49:21.39,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.93,0:49:28.93,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA F yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.94,0:49:41.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Go now!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.15,0:49:48.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA growls]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:48.92,0:49:50.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE yells]
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.25,0:49:51.92,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.04,0:50:19.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You will die--!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.98,0:50:22.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA grunting]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.39,0:50:27.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.06,0:50:32.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[HEAD FUUMA grunts]
Dialogue: 0,0:50:50.58,0:50:53.21,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Isame... Isame!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:54.68,0:50:56.05,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Stand up.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.08,0:50:57.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You have to get up now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:04.66,0:51:07.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] The master is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.23,0:51:10.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,From this day on, My brother and I are Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.00,0:51:20.94,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Kotarou Fuuma the 10th stands before you.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.97,0:51:23.44,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,If you object to this, the time to speak is now.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:30.75,0:51:33.22,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] We Fuuma serve Lord Orochi.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.25,0:51:36.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Together, we'll mold our future.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.16,0:51:38.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,One where fear has no place.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.03,0:51:44.50,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isame. We're still one in the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.53,0:51:48.33,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,My life is yours. Yours is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:48.37,0:51:49.40,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:52.67,0:51:54.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] We were so certain...
Dialogue: 0,0:51:54.31,0:51:55.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,So full of hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:00.51,0:52:01.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.71,0:52:02.98,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.45,0:52:06.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Think you're gonna make it?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.23,0:52:19.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Where did it go off course?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.17,0:52:25.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Tenka Kumou's passing is a blessing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:25.14,0:52:28.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Our most troublesome pawn taken off the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.11,0:52:30.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Indeed. Most troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.61,0:52:34.35,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,His death certainly does make things simpler.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:37.08,0:52:39.65,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Lord Orochi's vessel is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.69,0:52:41.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Now is the time for action.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.79,0:52:46.79,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] Isuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.83,0:52:48.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Are we still one in the same?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.66,0:52:54.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] We are Kotarou Fuuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.10,0:52:55.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,It won't be long now, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:55.67,0:52:56.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.54,0:53:03.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[door opens, closes]
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.24,0:53:07.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISAME] My life is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.45,0:53:08.68,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,is yours mine?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:11.68,0:53:13.59,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] I see it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:13.62,0:53:16.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How so much of his life was spent caged.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.52,0:53:19.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I barely made it seven days in that box.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.09,0:53:21.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The isolation changes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:26.73,0:53:28.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Father... Mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.87,0:53:32.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Isame...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.44,0:53:35.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How could I liken my fear to his?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:49.16,0:53:50.56,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[coughs]
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.90,0:54:03.20,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] I lived.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.81,0:54:07.77,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The mission was a failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.81,0:54:10.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I lost my brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.14,0:54:12.25,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How is it I'm still drawing breath?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:16.92,0:54:19.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I was a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:19.52,0:54:21.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The strength of family is potent.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:24.89,0:54:27.19,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I envy the life of Shirasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:33.80,0:54:36.27,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Who's there? Show yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.51,0:54:45.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] The dream is gone, as is my purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:45.58,0:54:46.88,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I am without meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.55,0:54:51.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SURVIVOR FUUMA A] Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.75,0:54:53.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You survived.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.65,0:54:55.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,As did you.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.76,0:54:57.72,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,We're the only ones left, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.76,0:54:59.73,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sir, many of us are hurt.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.76,0:55:02.13,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SURVIVOR FUUMA C] We require guidance, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.36,0:55:05.23,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SURVIVOR FUUMA B] Please help us, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.24,0:55:14.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Is the child yours?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.84,0:55:16.18,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[FUUMA MOTHER A] Yes, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.21,0:55:17.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,He was born not long ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:19.95,0:55:22.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The Fuuma clan shall endure this.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.42,0:55:25.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,You're alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:25.65,0:55:27.62,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Follow me if you wish to keep living.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.29,0:55:34.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[ISUKE] Make shelter the first priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.79,0:55:35.76,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[GROUP] Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.47,0:55:46.51,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Brother... Your life is mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:52.01,0:55:54.41,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,And my life is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.08,0:59:11.84,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] What's captured your attention?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:11.88,0:59:12.85,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.08,0:59:15.58,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,The sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:15.61,0:59:18.12,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Didn't know it could get that blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.15,0:59:20.55,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Sounds like someone's missing the clouds.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.59,0:59:22.52,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I wouldn't go that far, Kiiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.56,0:59:25.49,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Though cloudy skies do tend to make me nostalgic.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:28.03,0:59:30.03,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I'd really like some more of this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.60,0:59:32.63,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[KIIKO] Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:32.67,0:59:35.07,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Excuse me! Can I get another ten skewers
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.10,0:59:36.57,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,of dango over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:36.60,0:59:38.10,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,How are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:38.14,0:59:39.81,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA chuckles]
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.84,0:59:43.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[TENKA] Soramaru, Chutaro, Shirasu.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:43.81,0:59:46.45,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Nothing but laughs over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.48,0:59:47.95,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Hope you can say the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.86,0:59:57.06,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What now?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.76,1:00:03.00,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[YAMAGATA] Are you certain?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.03,1:00:04.53,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,What is it, Nishiki?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:06.70,1:00:07.87,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[SOSEI] I am.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.90,1:00:10.64,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,I can provide the necessary information.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:10.67,1:00:13.04,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,[YAMAGATA] Excellent. Please do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.07,1:00:16.11,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Your experience with the Yamainu is beneficial.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:16.14,1:00:18.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,Welcome to the Orochi experiment...
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.91,1:00:21.78,OP Lyrics - English,,0,0,0,,...Sosei Abeno.
